c Every comment line starts with "c ".
c The weight format here is UNWEIGHTED.

c The problem line has the form "p cnf $numVars $numClauses":
p cnf 2 3

c Every literal has weight 1.

c Every clause line lists literals and ends with "0".

c A clause line for the positive literal x1:
1 0

c A clause line for the negative literal -x2:
-2 0

c A clause line for the disjunction x1 \/ -x2:
1 -2 0
